    "The higher the IOU threshold, the more difficult an object is to detect.",
    "IOU with different threshold values is usually selected in experiments to comprehensively test the model's performance.",
    "Definition 7 Dataset Preprocessing: Dataset preprocessing consists of two main steps:",
    "data collection and data segmentation.",
    "In order to collect data, researchers can use publicly available datasets, like UCF101 (Soomro et al. 2012) and AVA (Gu et al. 2018) mentioned in Sect. 2.2, or they can obtain data through specialized video and sensor collection equipment."
